ds a team of 20 researchers working on projects involving genomics analysis, drug discovery, and treatment optimization. Their work has resulted in several breakthrough publications in Nature Medicine and The New England Journal of Medicine.\n\nTechNova\'s expansion continued in 2022 with the opening of international offices in London, England, and Toronto, Canada. The London office, managed by Regional Director Emma Thompson, focuses on serving the European market and navigating complex regulatory requirements under GDPR and MDR regulations. The Toronto office, led by Regional Director David Kim, serves as the entry point for the Canadian healthcare market and collaborates closely with Health Canada for regulatory compliance.\n'}], 'model': 'gpt-4o', 'max_tokens': 3000, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.0}}
